Description: Ibanez RG Reverse gunmetal with 24v EMGs, brass trem block, and Gotoh tuners! Very nice condition, besides the small chip by the upper strap button. This is an RG320 body with a RG5EX1 reverse headstock and pewter inlays. Neck and frets are flawless! It is a wizard III neck. No cracks at the nut screws, no damage. Very nice. Plays amazing. Has a licensed floyd rose low profile tremolo with 34mm fat brass block. Fits the routing great and is better than the lo pro edge these usually come with. Installed an EMG 81/85 solderless kit and upgraded to a 24v battery. The 85 is in the bridge to give it a more aggressive sound. Can be easily swapped around but it's way more shred/metal worthy this way. The Gotoh tuners are great, very precise and smooth. Will come with the rear cavity covers, I just removed them for pics. Built this as a one of a kind, and it's a killer beast of a guitar. You will not find one like this anywhere else I can almost guarantee that. Will ship in a gig bag and double boxed. Via USPS Priority Mail. Insured. THANKS FOR VIEWING MESSAGE ME FOR MORE INFO OR PICS NO INTERNATIONAL SHIPPING 48 STATES ONLY
